# accommodation-api

accommodation-api is a simple API allowing consumers to view all the types of accommodation facilities provided by Universty of Rajshahi(RU) . It also allows the users to view all the students hall names and primary contact number for those halls, and also let the consumers to peek a view at the notices regarding all types of accommodations.  

## Types of accommodations [/accommodations]

### List of All Types of Accomodations [GET /accommodations]
Shows all types of accommodation facility RU provides
