### Enlist A New Type of Accommodation [POST /accommodations]
In case RU provides new kind of accommodation facility admin can add them


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "typo": "resthouse"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

           {
                "id":5,
                "typo" : "resthouse",
                "created_at" : "2017-07-23T21:28:06.162Z",
                "updated_at" : "2017-07-23T21:28:06.162Z"
            }
### Edit [PUT /accommodations/{id}]

Admin Edit the fields if it necessary
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/accommodations/5
    + Body

            {
                "typo": "house"
            }
+ Response 204

### Delete [DELETE /accommodations/{id}]

Admin can delete fields if it is necessary

+ Request
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/accommodations/5
+ Response 204

