### Enlist A New Students' Hall[POST /students_halls]
In case RU a new Hall is built admin can add it to the list.
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id" : 6,
            "names" : "Matihar Hall",
            "contact_no" : "0721-711192 (Md. Ali Asgar,Provost)
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "id" : 6,
                "names" : "Matihar Hall",
                "contact_no" : "0721-711192 (Md. Ali Asgar,Provost)",
                "created_at" : "2017-07-23T22:54:30.277Z",
                "updated_at" : "2017-07-23T22:54:30.277Z"
            }

### Edit [PUT /students_halls/{id}]

Admin Edit the fields if it is necessary like in a situtation  where the contact number is changed
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/students_halls/6
    + Body

            {
                "contact_no" : "0721-0000000 (Md. Ali Asgar,Provost)"
            }
+ Response 204

### Delete [DELETE /students_halls/{id}]

Admin can delete fields if it is necessary. Suppose a situation arise where a hall is no longer in use.

+ Request
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/students_halls/6
+ Response 204

## Notice Regarding Accommodations [/notices]
### All Notices [GET /notices]
Shows all the available notices regarding Accommodations.
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id" : 1,
                "notice_for" : "Sher-e Bangla Fazlul Haque Hall",
                "details" : "Hall Admision",
                "important_dates" : "Starts: 8.8.14 Ends: 15.9.15",
                "attachments_needed" : "photo, id card",
                "created_at" : "2017-07-23T17:40:22.080Z",
                "updated_at" : "2017-07-23T17:40:22.080Z"
                }
        ]

### Hang A New Notice[POST /notices]
Admin can post a new notice if necessary.

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "notice_for" : "foreign dorms",
                "details" : "Vacant dorms for Ramadan Holidays",
                "important_dates" : "Last date: 15.6.17",
                "attachments_needed" : "N/A",
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "id" : 2,
                "notice_for" : "foreign dorms",
                "details" : "Vacant dorms for Ramadan Holidays",
                "important_dates" : "Last date: 15.6.17",
                "attachments_needed" : "N/A",
                "created_at" : "2017-07-23T23:40:34.237Z",
                "updated_at" : "2017-07-23T23:40:34.237Z"
            }

### Edit [PUT /notices/{id}]

Admin Edit a notice if it is necessary
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/notices/2
    + Body

            {
                "important_dates" : "Last date: 20.6.17"
            }
+ Response 204

### Delete [DELETE /notices/{id}]

Admin can delete a notice if necessary, for example, in a situation where the notice is no longer valid

+ Request
    + Headers

            Location: http://localhost:3000/notices/2
+ Response 204
